Eyeforenergy is pleased to announce that one of our sponsoring publications, Risk in Focus (www.riskinfocus.com) has just agreed to sponsor 5 tickets to the upcoming Energy Exchanges Online Europe conference taking place in Amsterdam, February 19-21st at the Hotel Okura.


This means we have 5 tickets to give away at noon (GMT) on Friday.


With speakers from Powergen, Bergen Energi, RWE Trading, Endesa, El Paso, the European Energy Exchange, the UK Power Exchange, and the Amsterdam Power Exchange to name a few, this event is your opportunity to get the lastest news on the energy trading industry.  With the recent changes in the industry, can you afford not to be networking with your peers at this crucial time?


For more information on the conference simply go to www.eyeforenergy.com/freedraw and fill in your contact details.  Recipients will be notified by 1pm GMT on Friday 25th January.


See you in Amsterdam!


The Eyeforenergy Team.
